column2: SELECT TOP #  gal.psfMag_u, gal.psfMag_g, gal.psfMag_r, gal.psfMag_i, gal.psfMag_z,  gal.petroMag_u, gal.petroMag_g, gal.petroMag_r, gal.petroMag_i, gal.petroMag_z,  s.spectrotype, s.subclass, s.targettype FROM Galaxy AS gal  JOIN galSpecInfo AS s ON s.specObjID = gal.specObjID WHERE  s.targettype=&&&
